videos.description: Keith Stone battles his way through two defenders to score for Florida.
videos.headline: Chiozza finds Stone down court for layup

videos.description: Keith Stone picks up a big block to thwart a fast-break score for South Carolina.
videos.headline: Stone rises up to block a layup attempt

videos.description: Jalen Hudson strips the ball away and goes coast-to-coast to score for Florida.
videos.headline: Hudson turns steal into layup

videos.description: Evan Hinson steals an inbounds pass and jams it home on the other end for South Carolina.
videos.headline: Hinson jams it home after getting a steal

videos.description: KeVaughn Allen receives an inbounds pass and makes a 3-pointer through contact for Florida.
videos.headline: Allen drains 3-pointer plus a foul

videos.description: Wesley Myers' nice feed allows Chris Silva to hammer down a dunk for South Carolina.
videos.headline: Myers sets up two-handed jam for Silva

videos.description: Big performances from Chris Silva and Wesley Myers help the Gamecocks pick up a road win over the 20th ranked Gators.
videos.headline: 3-point shooting leads South Carolina to win over UF
